	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Once you get the bag from Aljuum, get 2 Young sonic wolf jawbones, they drop off of pups and wolflings in Hollowshade moor, put them in back and hit combine, you end up with Bloody Cloth Bag, No Drop.<BR>
<BR>
Give this to Aljuum Mohim in bar. loc is neg465 neg229.<BR>
<BR>
Aljuum Mohim Says &quot;How was your little encounter with those beasts? Quite nasty in combat, eh? I told you as much. Well, now that you've seen them firsthand, I'll tell you how to deal with them like a true hunter. Take this hilt piece and show Hana Sulm. She'll give you some sketches. Once you have those sketches, go to Arms Historian Qua and purchase the tomes on Wolf Bane Lore or something like that. He'll know what you mean. You can use those books and the sketches to make a weapon that offers considerable power against those wolves. Once you have the weapon, bring it back to me with your apprentice cloak. I'll have something for you. Now go away and let me finish this drink&quot;.<BR>
<BR>
Hana Sulm is located at neg482 neg320 real close to Aljuum. (dont you wish everyone kept such good notes? :P) Give her hilt piece.<BR>
<BR>
Hana Sulm says 'Well, you're going to need to practice for a while to make these things. Take these sketches and read up on the lore concerning sonic wolves. You'll learn how to use the sketches. Practice all you can. I'm sure you're going to have a lot of people coming to you with requests.'<BR>
Your faction standing with Guardians of Shar Vahl got better.<BR>
<BR>
Arms Historian Qua is at loc neg174 pos52 near palace on left when facing doors in front.<BR>
DONT give him sketches or hilt, he will keep em, Purchase the volumes from him.<BR>
<BR>
These books are somewhat confusing and the list of items is immense, prepare for a long road ahead of you. Items needed are as follows:<BR>
<BR>
blackened salt crystals<BR>
digested night palm<BR>
sonic wolf brain<BR>
Crystalized Ygri root<BR>
Salass Moss<BR>
tortoise saliva<BR>
sonic wolf blood x 4<BR>
poison dart from grunt shaman<BR>
owlbear and sonic bear tendons<BR>
kelp salt<BR>
fish oil soaked rags<BR>
vial of owlbear bile<BR>
black silt clay<BR>
quality firing sheet<BR>
white sands from marshlands<BR>
powdered wolf claws (when you loot these they are called powered, mispelled)<BR>
<BR>
this is all ingredients for all of the weapon, how to combine them is in the books, its somewhat riddled. good luck
				</font>
